Package com.example.mapme.view

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddMarkerActivity
    AddMarkerActivity - Activity to add marker to the map.
    AddObjectActivity
    AddObjectActivity - abstract Activity that provides all common methods for AddMarker, AddPolygon and AddPolyline Activities.
    AddPolygonActivity
    AddPolygonActivity - Activity to draw polygons on the map.
    AddPolylineActivity
    AddPolylineActivity - Activity to draw polylines on the map.
    DataActivity
    DataActivity - Activity to display data from database.
    EditInformationActivity
    EditInformationActivity - Activity to edit information for specific geoObject.
    MainActivity
    MainActivity - Start screen when opening the app.
    MapActivity
    MapActivity - Activity that shows map with geoObjects, user position and menu items.
